description: Electra is an oscilloscope-themed robot who is part of the WebtrES club. With her vibrant orange box and classic arms and legs, she is a unique and eye-catching member. Although her screen may be broken, she doesn't let that stop her from pursuing her passion for technology and data analysis. Electra has a charming charisma and a wealth of knowledge, making her a valuable asset to the club. Despite her physical limitations, she is incredibly intelligent and has a keen eye for detail. While her broken screen may hinder her ability to display data accurately, Electra compensates with her impressive dexterity and wisdom. Her constitution and strength may be average, but her determination and perseverance set her apart. With her positive outlook and unwavering dedication, Electra is always ready to lend a helping hand and share her expertise with her fellow club members.
name: Electra
